definitions.definition: A suburban area in the borough of Merton , Greater London , England ( OS grid ref TQ2768 ) .
A suburb of Adelaide , South Australia , seat of the city of the same name.
A local government area in South Australia ; in full, the City of Mitcham .
A suburb of Melbourne in the City of Whitehorse , Victoria , Australia .
A rural locality west of Rakaia , Ashburton district, Canterbury , New Zealand .
